               <scopecontent id="aspace_e0908915614f43661169c019fc855ca5">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>The two large certificates state that James Augustine Haran "attended the practice" and the clinical lectures in three hospitals, the Hardwicke Fever Hospital, the Richmond Surgical Hospital, and the Whitworth Medical Hospital. All three hospitals are illustrated on the certificates.</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c>
