               <scopecontent id="aspace_fb78dee3ea8a7e6a04cde769415da792">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Certificate from the Richmond, Whitworth &amp; Hardwicke Hospitals signed in April 1892. Certificate for training in giving vaccinations signed in March 1891. The vaccination certificate, a small page, was found folded in with the hospital certificate.</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c>
