                             localtype="box">1</container>
                  <container id="aspace_86a2210b712fd7a019793a418790d16f"
                             localtype="folder"
                             parent="aspace_e8fe0b2c8db6ca8d56628db72596ac94">11</container>
               </did>
               <scopecontent id="aspace_3e17789bced5c9d219ba972be3a0291b">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Kisumu (now Kisumu Town) is an inland port city on Lake Victoria, now part of Kenya. The 34x32 cm. map shows houses that were burnt and houses where the plague occurred.</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c>
