               </did>
               <scopecontent id="aspace_b89d52d9fe522119bc8f947a139aeac5">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Typed letter conveys the satisfaction of His Majesty's Secretary of State for the Colonies for the work that Haran had done in combating the recent outbreak of plague.</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c>
