               <scopecontent id="aspace_4fb3f1c039158694ca26066a910e6540">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Large broadside explaining what the plague is and the precautions to take. Printed by the Government Printer, Accra, Gold Coast Colony, West Africa. The Gold Coast was a British colony on the Gulf of Guinea in West Africa. It is now Ghana.</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c>
