                  <p>Carbon of a typescript emended in ink. Also a handwritten letter on the stationary of the East Africa Protectorate on the politics of management of Mombasa and mosquitoes. The writer is unidentified and appears to have written the typed manuscript. Both items were sent in an envelope (present in the folder) to Haran in Mombasa.</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c>
